Description: In this video, we tried to push the limits of the RTX 5090 GPU to achieve 1,000 FPS in the video game Doom. We experimented with various settings, including DLSS frame generation and upscaling, to try to reach this goal. However, it seems we are CPU-limited, and despite the power of the 5090, we were unable to consistently hit the 1,000 FPS mark. We're now looking for suggestions on what other games we should try to test the limits of this powerful GPU.  #ryankennedy #gaming
